summary:
Worked for Shell for 19 years (Aberdeen & Pernis, Netheralnds) as Chemical Analist (HLO Laboratorium opleiding). Moved to Singapore in 2005 and obtained ITEC certificate in Anatomy Physiology & Holistic Massage, also practitioner for Raindrop Technique.
I am an English native speaker with an abundance of work and social experience in the UK, 
Netherlands and Singapore. I feel I have accumulated several different skills that could be 
beneficial within your company. Communication, Team Working, Organising and Planning
are a few skills I would like to elaborate on. With my work experience I have been able to
show my written and spoken skills in both the English and Dutch language, specifically
through reporting, presenting, supporting and motivating others. 
As a former Self Employed Wellness Coach (Dutch) I also feel I have enough enthusiasm to make things
happen, have a hands on attitude, achieve goals and accept responsibilities for my actions.
I am now looking for a new challenge be it in the laboratory world, administration, customer care or anything related to the English language.
